definitions.definition: The name of various cities, towns and boroughs in the USA , United Kingdom , Canada , Australia and New Zealand . See the full list .
examples: This year, I'll be going to Stratford on holiday. I heard it's lovely in May.

subdefinitions.definition: A suburb of Cairns , Queensland , Australia .
A town on the Avon in Victoria , Australia .
A rural locality in MidCoast council area, New South Wales , Australia .
A town in Taranaki , New Zealand .
A city on the Avon in Ontario , Canada .
A town in Queens County , Prince Edward Island , Canada .
A township municipality in Estrie , Quebec , Canada .

A place in England : A town in the borough of Newham , Greater London ( OS grid ref TQ3884 ) . A market town in Stratford-upon-Avon parish, Stratford-on-Avon district, Warwickshire , properly Stratford-upon-Avon . A hamlet in Sandy parish, Central Bedfordshire , Bedfordshire ( OS grid ref TL1847 ) . A hamlet in Ripple parish, Malvern Hills district, Worcestershire , on the border with Gloucestershire ( OS grid ref SO8838 ) .

Places in the United States : A census-designated place in Kings County , California . A town in Fairfield County , Connecticut . An unincorporated community in Ogle County , Illinois . A small city in Hamilton County and Webster County , Iowa . A small town in Coos County , New Hampshire . A borough of Camden County , New Jersey . A small town in Fulton County , New York . An unincorporated community in Delaware County , Ohio . A town in Garvin County , Oklahoma . A tiny town in Brown County , South Dakota . A small city , the county seat of Sherman County , Texas . An unincorporated community in Grant County , Washington . A village in Marathon County , Wisconsin .
